ABSTRACT
Disclosed are systems and methods for improving interac-
tions with and between computers in content searching,
generating, hosting and/or providing systems supported by
or configured with personal computing devices, servers
and/or platforms. The systems interact to identify and
retrieve data within or across platforms, which can be used
to improve the quality of data used in processing interactions
between or among processors in such systems. The disclosed
systems and methods automatically determine media con-
tent to communicate to a user based on the user's location.
The disclosed systems and methods enable novel media
content distribution to a user based on 1) the location of the
user (i.e., physical location or geo-location), 2) other users'
classified relationships to the location; and 3) user generated
media content by the classified other users.
